"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hkh1665702770516.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hkh1665702770516.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hkh1665702770516.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hkh1665702770516\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This method calls the accept trigger. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__topic_d128735e1_d128736e1_d128737e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__p_d128738e1_d128739e1_d128740e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">import\n               com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__p_d128741e1_d128742e1_d128743e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int accept() throws UnifaceException;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__section_vyk_rvv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1232399e64\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__p_d128747e1_d128748e1_d128749e1\">Returns <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> or, in the event\n            of an error, throws a UnifaceException.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__section_d23_tvv_cwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1232399e76\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hkh1665702770516__p_d128753e1_d128754e1_d128755e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">accept</code> method in the generated\n            Java, or JavaBean, file calls the accept trigger/operation in the Uniface component.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kez1665702582531.html\" stylesp